A Chromium extension to allow note-taking for web pages.

Hit a shortcut key on any web page, and a text box will pop up.
In the textbox you can enter notes, then push a "Save" button below to save them.

If you visit a page that has associated notes, the text box will pop up automatically.

The shortcut key _toggles_ visibility of the text box.

You can also to to an about: page to search for saved notes by URL (regex).


